msgstr ""

#: ../../../gpu-programming/launching-kernels.md:269
msgid ""
"The block size is the single most important tuning parameter (see the {ref}"
"`Execution Model <execution-choosing-block-size>` chapter for details). "
"Quick guidelines:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../gpu-programming/launching-kernels.md:273
msgid "**256** is a safe default for most kernels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../gpu-programming/launching-kernels.md:274
msgid "**Powers of 2** (128, 256, 512) align with warp boundaries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../gpu-programming/launching-kernels.md:275
